final_desc: - Lesitin dan fosfoaminolipid lainnya :Garam dan hidroksida amonium kuarterner; lesitin dan fosfoaminolipid lainnya, mempunyai rumus kimia tertentu maupun tidak.;- Lecithins and other phosphoaminolipids :Quaternary ammonium salts and hydroxides; lecithins and other phosphoaminolipids, whether or not chemically defined.
